Write 3 things that you&#039;ve seen someone do in your games, one of which is made up. We guess which is the fake. Might as well get some mileage out of the absurdity of soloq.

1. Full damage Udyr top screaming at Kha jungle &quot;build tank we need a tank!&quot;
2. Vayne: &quot;Report Tryndamere ulted himself instead of me!&quot;
3. Blitz (who already has a frozen heart) screaming at jungler  for not building frozen heart. Enemy team is mostly AP.
